title: JULIA AND BECCA WANT TO HELP YOU GET LAID!
description: This week on The Shitshow Julia and Becca want to help get you laid on vacation, because who doesn’t like having sex in exotic places? Even if it's just a stayvaction somewhere close, don’t be afraid to mix things up! Listen as the two friends share their personal experiences and some of their wild stories abroad, like that time Becca bit a stripper on the ass, or maybe how they almost died in Tulum with the Nelk boys… All bets are off the table. Shirts are off too, so don't forget to check out the video on YouTube this Thursday!
